        <item>
            <title>0.2.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                  <li>One-click install: click <b>Install in ValueGuard</b> on the config directory and a policy downloads, verifies, and appears in the new <b>Configs</b> settings tab — no terminal.</li>
                  <li>vgconfig:// URL scheme + trust-confirmation sheet (author key fingerprint, registry origin, categories, offline-verified badge).</li>
                  <li>Auto-update support (this build and later update automatically).</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
